00:00:00.130 --> 00:00:01.538
Previously on Haven:

2
00:00:01.798 --> 00:00:02.706
Duke Crocker.

3
00:00:02.966 --> 00:00:05.458
Somebody out there with a tattoo
wants to kill me.

4
00:00:05.718 --> 00:00:06.293
This is Evi.

5
00:00:06.413 --> 00:00:07.847
I'm Duke's wife.

6
00:00:07.967 --> 00:00:09.575
Last thing Haven needs...

7
00:00:09.833 --> 00:00:13.192
is the Rev and his self-righteous poison
running things.

8
00:00:13.312 --> 00:00:14.301
He wants to be chief?

9
00:00:14.561 --> 00:00:16.159
He wants to control whoever is.

10
00:00:16.279 --> 00:00:19.222
Nathan. your father. he chose
to live among the cursed.

11
00:00:19.698 --> 00:00:21.099
Seek forgiveness.

12
00:00:21.359 --> 00:00:22.559
I can help you.

13
00:00:22.819 --> 00:00:23.832
I need to know more her.

14
00:00:23.952 --> 00:00:25.353
Lucy Ripley.

15
00:00:25.421 --> 00:00:26.554
What do you think?
She your mother?

16
00:00:26.622 --> 00:00:28.189
I am Lucy.

17
00:00:28.257 --> 00:00:29.457
You can't save everyone.

18
00:00:29.525 --> 00:00:31.592
But that's why I'm here.

19
00:00:37.433 --> 00:00:40.268
♪ cold and dark
below the foam ♪

20
00:00:40.335 --> 00:00:43.571
♪ they wait for us
but never alone ♪

21
