♪ the sea is dark
the sea is deep ♪

22
00:00:47.342 --> 00:00:51.179
♪ down below is
where they sleep ♪

23
00:00:51.246 --> 00:00:53.981
♪ cold and dark
below the foam ♪

24
00:00:54.049 --> 00:00:58.186
♪ they wait for us
but never alone ♪

25
00:00:58.253 --> 00:01:00.321
- Aah!
- No!

26
00:01:00.389 --> 00:01:01.389
Let me go!

27
00:01:01.457 --> 00:01:02.824
Stop!
I don't want to!

28
00:01:02.891 --> 00:01:04.025
Please!

29
00:01:04.093 --> 00:01:05.093
No!

30
00:01:09.064 --> 00:01:10.098
No!

